Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: "Early mail-in voting is underway now in Michigan—so go out and get that ballot, return it as soon as possible—and if not, get a ballot, vote... get as many other Trump supporters as you can and they'll do the same!33 days from now, we are going to WIN the state of Michigan, we are going to defeat Lyin’ Kamala Harris... and we are going to MAKE AMERICA GREAT AGAIN."
